---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="our story — green°">

<!-- Hero -->
<header class="os-hero">
  <span class="gn-eyebrow os-hero__eyebrow">our story</span>
  <h1 class="os-hero__title">creatively<br>crafting <em>change.</em></h1>
</header>

<!-- Story body -->
<article class="os-body">

  <p>In December 2019 we created green° to sustainably raise funds for education in South Africa. We had been made aware of the fact that many children had no access to basic required stationery. We wanted to assist these children, have a positive impact on the environment and in the communities we worked in.</p>

  <p>We had our first fundraising function, a small gathering of friends and family where we collected old denim and raised R12,000 in the form of pencil case sponsorship and so began a creative, challenging and uplifting journey…</p>

  <div class="os-pull">
    <p class="os-pull__text">We raised awareness that evening of the excessive water used in the denim manufacturing process, the dreadful pollution left behind and how much of this still strong and usable material ended up in landfill.</p>
  </div>

  <p>In discovering this we became aware of a unique opportunity and challenge to creatively and sustainably raise funds, while saving waste material from landfill and creating employment and awareness of the environmental crisis. Using the Sewing Cafe in Masiphumelele we made our first 500 pencil cases and filled them with stationery.</p>

  <hr class="os-rule">

  <p>Year on year green° has grown on all fronts. Today we collect a multitude of different waste fabrics. To raise funds we design and develop beautiful, functional upcycled products best suited to these materials. We employ local craftsmen, training initiatives and community collaboratives to hand make our designs which are available at our annual open day.</p>

  <p>100% of all profits go into supplying required stationery and pencil cases to children at Capricorn, Caravelle and Westlake Primary Schools.</p>

  <p>In 2020 we assisted 500 children. This January 2025 we assisted 2,550 children. Annually we go to each school and hand out to each child, developing a good working relationship within the schools that we sponsor, and ensuring we supply what is most needed.</p>

  <div class="os-pull">
    <p class="os-pull__text">Feedback from the schools is that there is a significant impact on the learners' ability to engage and a noticeable improvement in pride of their work. Pupils are more motivated knowing they have the tools to participate in assignments. Teachers also report boosted confidence, increased workflow and less disruptions in the classroom.</p>
  </div>

  <p>We have worked hard and had a challenging, inspiring and rewarding journey so far. We'd never be able to do this without our families, friends, and the community — those who donate, purchase, support and collaborate.</p>

</article>

<!-- Mission -->
<section class="os-mission">
  <div class="os-mission__inner">
    <div class="os-mission__label">
      <span class="gn-eyebrow os-mission__eyebrow">mission</span>
      <h2 class="os-mission__title">rooted in sustainability<br>and care.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="os-mission__copy">
      <p>At green°, we believe every child deserves the chance to learn, grow and thrive. We raise funds to support under-resourced primary schools. By forming long-term, meaningful relationships with our beneficiaries we can help ensure that every contribution meets a real need and makes a lasting difference.</p>
      <p>Our mission is rooted in sustainability and care. We repurpose waste materials into beautiful, functional products using the hands and talents of local artisans and community members. In doing so, we reduce waste, support livelihoods and create products that tell a story of hope and possibility.</p>
      <p>We champion conscious consumerism by inviting people to make choices that honour the planet and uplift communities. Every item we sell helps equip a child for the classroom, and every act of support helps build a better future for us all.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Values -->
<section class="os-values">
  <div class="os-values__head">
    <span class="gn-eyebrow">values</span>
    <h2 class="os-values__title">what guides us.</h2>
  </div>
  <ol class="os-values__list">
    <li class="os-values__item">
      <span class="os-values__num">01</span>
      <span class="os-values__name">sustainability</span>
    </li>
    <li class="os-values__item">
      <span class="os-values__num">02</span>
      <span class="os-values__name">support &amp; uplift local</span>
    </li>
    <li class="os-values__item">
      <span class="os-values__num">03</span>
      <span class="os-values__name">kindness</span>
    </li>
  </ol>
</section>

<!-- Invitation close -->
<section class="os-invite">
  <div class="os-invite__inner">
    <span class="gn-eyebrow os-invite__eyebrow">the invitation</span>
    <blockquote class="os-invite__quote">
      we invite everyone to please join us, and become part of the green<span class="gn-deg">°</span> story.
    </blockquote>
    <a href="/donate" class="os-invite__cta">donate →</a>
  </div>
</section>


</Layout>

<style>
/* Hero */
.os-hero {
  max-width: var(--page-max);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 144px var(--page-pad) 80px;
}
.os-hero__eyebrow { margin-bottom: 32px; }
.os-hero__title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 300;
  font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6.5rem);
  line-height: 0.98;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  color: var(--color-ink);
  margin: 0;
  max-width: 14ch;
  text-wrap: balance;
}
.os-hero__title em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--color-sage-deep);
}
@media (max-width: 720px) { .os-hero { padding: 64px var(--page-pad-mobile) 48px; } }

/* Story body */
.os-body {
  max-width: 720px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 var(--page-pad) 120px;
}
.os-body p {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  margin: 0 0 1.6em;
  text-wrap: pretty;
}
.os-body p:first-of-type {
  font-size: 20px;
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: var(--color-ink);
}

/* Pull quote */
.os-pull {
  border-left: 2px solid var(--color-lime);
  padding: 8px 0 8px 28px;
  margin: 56px 0;
}
.os-pull__text {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 300;
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
  line-height: 1.2;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  color: var(--color-ink);
  margin: 0;
  text-wrap: pretty;
}

/* Divider */
.os-rule {
  border: 0;
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--color-rule);
  margin: 72px 0;
}

@media (max-width: 720px) {
  .os-body { padding: 0 var(--page-pad-mobile) 80px; }
  .os-body p { font-size: 16px; }
}

/* Mission */
.os-mission {
  background: var(--color-bg-tint);
  padding: 96px 0;
}
.os-mission__inner {
  max-width: var(--page-max);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding-inline: var(--page-pad);
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
  gap: 80px;
  align-items: start;
}
.os-mission__label {
  position: sticky;
  top: 48px;
}
.os-mission__eyebrow { margin-bottom: 20px; }
.os-mission__title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 300;
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
  line-height: 1.08;
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  color: var(--color-ink);
  margin: 0;
}
.os-mission__copy { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
.os-mission__copy p {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 17px;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  margin: 0 0 1.6em;
  text-wrap: pretty;
}
@media (max-width: 820px) {
  .os-mission { padding: 64px 0; }
  .os-mission__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; padding-inline: var(--page-pad-mobile); }
  .os-mission__label { position: static; }
}

/* Values */
.os-values {
  max-width: var(--page-max);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 96px var(--page-pad) 120px;
}
.os-values__head {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 24px;
  padding-bottom: 40px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
  margin-bottom: 0;
}
.os-values__title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 300;
  font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  color: var(--color-ink);
  margin: 0;
}
.os-values__list { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
.os-values__item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 24px;
  padding: 32px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
}
.os-values__num {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 300;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  color: var(--color-ink-faint);
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 2.5ch;
}
.os-values__name {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 300;
  font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  color: var(--color-ink);
  line-height: 1;
}
@media (max-width: 720px) {
  .os-values { padding: 64px var(--page-pad-mobile) 80px; }
  .os-values__item { padding: 24px 0; }
}

/* Invitation close */
.os-invite {
  background: var(--color-ink);
  padding: 120px var(--page-pad) 100px;
  text-align: center;
}
.os-invite__inner { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
.os-invite__eyebrow {
  color: rgba(232,225,203,0.6);
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}
.os-invite__quote {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 300;
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  line-height: 1.08;
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  color: var(--color-bg);
  margin: 0 0 48px;
  text-wrap: balance;
}
.os-invite__cta {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  text-transform: lowercase;
  padding: 16px 28px;
  background: var(--color-lime);
  color: var(--color-ink);
  text-decoration: none;
  border: none;
  transition: background 200ms;
}
.os-invite__cta:hover { background: #bfe070; color: var(--color-ink); }
@media (max-width: 720px) { .os-invite { padding: 80px var(--page-pad-mobile) 64px; } }

/* Footer */
.os-foot {
  background: var(--color-ink);
  padding: 32px var(--page-pad);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
}
.os-foot__copy {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: rgba(232,225,203,0.4);
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}
.os-foot__back {
  color: rgba(232,225,203,0.4);
  text-decoration: none;
  border: none;
  transition: color 160ms;
}
.os-foot__back:hover { color: var(--color-bg); }
.os-foot__dot {
  width: 5px;
  height: 5px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--color-lime);
}
@media (max-width: 720px) {
  .os-foot { padding: 24px var(--page-pad-mobile); flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; text-align: center; }
}
</style>
